MorseCodeClient
The MorseCodeClient class is a class that represents a client that will be used to communicate Morse Code with another client

The MorseCodeServer class is a class that represents a server that will create a connection with 2 clients to allow them to be able to communicate with each other via Morse Code
MorseCodeServerTest
The MorseCodeServerTest is a class that is used to run a server.
MorseCodeTranslator
The MorseCodeTranslator class is a class that translates plain text to Morse code and pain text to Morse code
